projects.title: BMinor Compiler
projects.subtitle: GitLab Project | C | Flex | Bison
projects.description: The goal of this project is to create a compiler from scratch using C, Flex, and Bison to process BMinor files and output x86 assembly. This assembly, in turn, will be able to be assembled into an object file and then transformed into an executable.

projects.title: Hummingbird
projects.subtitle: GitLab Project | Python | CherryPy | JS | Bootstrap | HTML | CSS
projects.description: The goal of this project was to create a simulation of a stock trading platform. The server was initialized using CherryPy to handle client requests and return formatted data about real-time stocks. This server used RapidAPI's YahooFinance API to handle real-time data.

projects.title: DiscreetOctupus
projects.subtitle: GitLab Project | C | Shell | Python
projects.description: A web server built from scratch using parent/child processes, HTTP protocols, socket and port manipulation, and memory management. This project was initially the final project for CSE 20289, but it was forked at the end to be further enhanced and to be used as a personal server to host this website. Eventually, in Winter 2019, the website was redesigned and moved to a more common framework.
